--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
The 5ish AC he gets from the AGI buff is Avoidance AC (Avoidance AC comes only from AGI and Defense). Armor and buffs other than AGI provide Mitigation AC.<br>
<br>
It might result in one or two attacks against him being misses instead of hits during the full duration of the buff.<br>
<br>
There is no effect 'beyond' the AC effect. <br>
